      "content": "wait a perforated eardrum?? that sounds scary. do you really think it's that bad? i don't feel any actual pain, just that muffled feeling like my ear is under water. i'm in oslo and the clinics are all super expensive/busy right now. could it just be a temporary thing where the pressure is just stuck? like if i try to pop my ears or use some ear drops it'll just clear up?",
