      "content": "i hear you, but inflamming things by going to the hospital seems like a lot for just a muffled ear. the pressure thing feels so obvious though... like i can literally feel the air trapped in there. if i just wait a day or two to see if the pressure equalizes on its own, is that really going to make a huge difference? it's probably just a minor thing that'll resolve itself once the ear settles down, right?",
